{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "End the 2023 \u00a3476m deal with France to stop the migrants crossing the channel",
        "additional_details": "There are reports that the French police are allowing the migrants to leave French shores and offering no resistance, so stopping the payments will send a clear message to the French Government that we expect results.",
        "background": "Stop paying the French Government the money that we believe isn\u2019t being used effectively to stop the migrants. We believe that the French are in effect reneging on the 2023 agreement.",
